**Luna Node**

&lt;a href="https://lunanode.com/" target="_blank"&gt;Luna Node&lt;/a&gt; provides high quality unmanaged VPS hosting at an affordable price. We exclusively use KVM on all plans for the greater control that it gives users. At the moment we're offering various plans in Chicago with 512 MB to 8192 MB memory. We take payments through PayPal (either through PayPal account or credit card) and **&lt;a href="http://bitcoin.org/" target="_blank"&gt;Bitcoin&lt;/a&gt;**.

Budget VPS and Plus KVM plans come with RAID10 HDD storage, and can be assigned 5 IPv4 addresses (/29) for an additional $0.75/month or 13 IPv4 addresses (/28) for an additional $3.00/month (justification required). SSD KVM plans come with a single IPv4 address and SSD storage. SSD KVM is backed up weekly.

On Budget VPS, we offer a custom VM control panel that features the typical management options (although we're currently still using SolusVM for our SSD KVM plans). Servers are provisioned out of SingleHop's Chicago datacenter (CHI-2).

**All plans come with a free single-domain/wildcard AlphaSSL certificate (additional certificates are $2/yr).** cPanel VM licenses are available at $10/mo.

Custom ISO's are available if you open a ticket on all plans. Windows available on SSD KVM with BYOL.

&lt;a href="https://www.lunanode.com/budget.php" target="_blank"&gt;Order budget VPS&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="https://www.lunanode.com/ssdkvm.php" target="_blank"&gt;SSD KVM now!&lt;/a&gt; Or &lt;a href="https://www.lunanode.com/submitticket.php?step=2&amp;deptid=2" target="_blank"&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt; for questions. Upload your &lt;a href="http://lifehacker.com/180878/how-to-encrypt-your-email" target="_blank"&gt;PGP public key&lt;/a&gt; to our &lt;a href="https://lunanode.com/gpgmw/" target="_blank"&gt;PGP web interface&lt;/a&gt; to receive encrypted mail from us.

